title: John Mayer - Human Nature (From Michael Jackson Memorial 7/7/09)
description:
This is John Mayer performing Human Nature at the Michael Jackson Memorial on 7/7/09.  I've never really been a big fan of John Mayer but he blew me away with this performance.  In my opinion it was the best performance from the entire memorial.  If you have yet to hear this then I definitely suggest you give it a listen here 


RIP MJ!!!  Still can't believe he's gone.....
